        "username": "四邑漁農牧工商總會",
        "uid": "7113"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t我外公和我姨媽（我媽老爸和我媽姐姐）當年偷渡，來港，到達市區（好像是沙田，離新界及深圳最近的市區）即獲發香港身份證<br/>\n<br/>\n現在的西北部天水圍屯門元朗東涌大嶼山當時還沒開發，荃灣開發了，但KCR kowloon-canton rail九廣鐵路在東部，當時的人偷渡好像也是在東部為主，荃灣太偏西了<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly91cGxvYWQud2lraW1lZGlhLm9yZy93aWtpcGVkaWEvY29tbW9ucy90aHVtYi8xLzEyL0hvbmdfS29uZ19TaGFfVGluX0Rpc3RyaWN0X2xvY2F0b3JfbWFwLnN2Zy81MDBweC1Ib25nX0tvbmdfU2hhX1Rpbl9EaXN0cmljdF9sb2NhdG9yX21hcC5zdmcuZ2lm\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/12/Hong_Kong_Sha_Tin_District_locator_map.svg/500px-Hong_Kong_Sha_Tin_District_locator_map.svg.gif\"><img alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/12/Hong_Kong_Sha_Tin_District_locator_map.svg/500px-Hong_Kong_Sha_Tin_District_locator_map.svg.gif\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/12/Hong_Kong_Sha_Tin_District_locator_map.svg/500px-Hong_Kong_Sha_Tin_District_locator_map.svg.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n當時最北的市區應該是沙田新市鎮（上）和荃灣市（下）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly91cGxvYWQud2lraW1lZGlhLm9yZy93aWtpcGVkaWEvY29tbW9ucy90aHVtYi85Lzk1L0hvbmdfS29uZ19Uc3Vlbl9XYW5fRGlzdHJpY3RfbG9jYXRvcl9tYXAuc3ZnLzUwMHB4LUhvbmdfS29uZ19Uc3Vlbl9XYW5fRGlzdHJpY3RfbG9jYXRvcl9tYXAuc3ZnLmdpZg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/95/Hong_Kong_Tsuen_Wan_District_locator_map.svg/500px-Hong_Kong_Tsuen_Wan_District_locator_map.svg.gif\"><img alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/95/Hong_Kong_Tsuen_Wan_District_locator_map.svg/500px-Hong_Kong_Tsuen_Wan_District_locator_map.svg.gif\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/95/Hong_Kong_Tsuen_Wan_District_locator_map.svg/500px-Hong_Kong_Tsuen_Wan_District_locator_map.svg.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
      "date": "2024-02-20",
